Components: Reusable building blocks in the web page, they must return JSX Format. there are 2 types of components:
1. Fucntional Components
2. Class Components

-1. Functional Components: The format which accepts data and return JSX.

code: 

function WelcomeMessage(props) {
  return <h1>Hello React.</h1>;
}

2. Class Components: It requires render() method (lifecycle method) to wrap ad return statement.

code: 


class Greeting extends Component {
  render() {
    // Reading from props and state, (prop- it carries the data)
    const name = this.props.name; 

    // Returning JSX elements
    return (
      <div>
        <h1>Hello, {name}!</h1>
        <p>Welcome back to the application.</p>
      </div>
    );
  }
}
